{"tid":681934,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"請擺脫「所有女人都唔係雞」呢個概念","createTime":"2018-05-28T12:30:28.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-29T05:50:06.000Z","uid":58335,"like":12,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"f43ac9a5b2c99b0297dcd30efa27a92753d1f446","tid":681934,"uid":58335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-28T12:30:28.000Z","msg":"而家連登咁多00後<br />\n佢地真係無思考能力<br />\n甚至一啲毒啲90後真係會認為呢個係事實<br />\n我身邊就有唔少<br />\n<br />\n我唔單止係為男性平反<br />\n更多嘅係唔想下一代有呢個思想<br />\n正如我地都唔希望下一代剩係識蝗語打拼音一樣<br />\n諗深少少 其實禍害一樣咁深<br />\n<br />\n而家幾乎每個人都會上連登<br />\n如果以後佢地真係擺脫唔到呢個思想<br />\n我想講 係我地造成 係我地親手害鳩左香港<br />\n<br />\n利申：90後連登仔 上連登見到有連登婆同狗公講所有女人都唔係雞"},{"pid":"fbcd02e7a5c998ebde74c1f0f42228430e9acc09","tid":681934,"uid":152753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-28T12:32:41.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">所有女人都唔係雞？</span></span>"},{"pid":"a2b1e76dcc4f04da916cc38606db63bfc0270305","tid":681934,"uid":64601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-28T12:33:11.000Z","msg":"得啦，有point啦"},{"pid":"1122aec5ed332101f61ae8e9c371fb821daa01a6","tid":681934,"uid":58335,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"fbcd02e7a5c998ebde74c1f0f42228430e9acc09","tid":681934,"uid":152753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-28T12:32:41.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">所有女人都唔係雞？</span></span>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-28T12:34:34.000Z","msg":"你要好好擺脫「所有女人都唔係雞」呢個概念啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa231f42f2af03204e6a6aa4ce78334deb10e53b","tid":681934,"uid":152753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fbcd02e7a5c998ebde74c1f0f42228430e9acc09","tid":681934,"uid":152753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-28T12:32:41.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">所有女人都唔係雞？</span></span>"},"citedBy":0,"reply